title: Tyler Mitchell, From Skateboarding to Photographing Beyoncé | Inside Fashion
itunes:title: Tyler Mitchell, From Skateboarding to Photographing Beyoncé | Inside Fashion
itunes:subtitle: Speaking in conversation with Imran Amed, the photographer behind Beyoncé's September 2018 Vogue cover talks identity, social media and how he found his way into fashion photography. You can watch Tyler's 2017 American Eagle campaign film here.Sign
description:
Speaking in conversation with Imran Amed, the photographer behind Beyoncé's September 2018 Vogue cover talks identity, social media and how he found his way into fashion photography.   You can watch Tyler's 2017 American Eagle campaign film here.
